  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>You'll be well fed at the Hotel Allalin, with the food consistently receiving top ratings in TripAdvisor reviews.</p>
<p>Start the day with an excellent daily buffet breakfast with hot options available.</p>
<p>In the afternoon there's free daily tea and coffee that can be enjoyed on the garden terrace.</p>
<p>A delicious five-course half board dinner is served in the beautifully rustic dining room, lined with 350-year-old larch wood and furnished with individually carved chairs. There is a choice of main course and a daily salad and cheese buffet.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
